	(1671,709,'ISD0611',104,1,'專題討論（二）','Seminar (II)',3984,'','','H',1,48,'',0,'','N',0,'1','',0,'','本部教室自排',NULL,'二1-2',0,'',NULL,20,0.4,0,50,2,'This seminar serves as a forum to foster a research culture in the department and discuss the theoretical and practical issues of conducting research and completing a graduate degree in Library and Information Science (LIS). For that purpose, the goal is in two-fold: to discuss and explore important research issues in LIS; to learn the practical skills of giving a presentation and writing a research paper. The course is organized as a number of lectures on giving presentations, writing papers, and other aspects of performing research and publishing papers, along with a number of invited research talks and colloquia. As such, all LIS master and PhD students are welcome and encouraged to attend the scheduled lectures, presentations, and colloquium.',0,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,0),
	(1672,798,'EPM0003',104,1,'教育行政學研究','Studies in Educational Administration',3985,'','','H',3,49,'',0,'','N',0,'','◎限碩一碩二碩三以上◎限博一博二博三博四博五以上修習',0,'','本部教801',NULL,'二2-4',0,'不開放上修',NULL,12,0.4,0,30,3,'一、教育行政學導論：教育行政的意義、範圍、研究方法、理論發展。 二、教育行政的功能：教育行政的計畫、決定、組織、領導、激勵、溝通、 評鑑（含視導）、興革。 三、教育行政的生態：組織文化、衝突管理、組織發展與興革。 四、教育行政制度：法令規定、教育行政組織。 五、教育行政人員：教育人員的培育、任用、倫理信條。 六、趨勢與展望：教育行政的發展趨勢與我國教育行政的展望。',0,20,20,0,0,0,0,0,0),
