	(2517,3017,'ESU0047',104,1,'宇宙觀的進展','The Development of Cosmology',4521,'','','H',3,91,'',0,'3','N',0,'1','◎限大三大四修習',0,'','公館Ｓ407',NULL,'一2-4',0,'',NULL,20,0.4,2,50,3,'The aim of this course is to introduce the students to the concepts of modern cosmology (General Relativity, Hubble Law, Primordial Nucleosynthesis, Cosmic Microwave Background, Dark matter and Dark Energy, Structure formation), and help them answer these questions: •What are the basic components of the universe? •What are the basic physical laws that govern the universe? •What is the size and age of the universe? •What\'s the current theory on origin and evolution of the universe (big bang!), and what are the evidences that support that theory? •What is the nature of space/time/matter/energy? •What about the \"dark side\" of the universe: black holes, cosmic dark ages, dark matter, dark energy? •How galaxies were formed? •What is a black-hole and what influence it has on galaxies? The first part of the course will be dedicated to introduce the students to these concepts via series of lecture, and in a second parts the student will practice their knowledge through research projects.',0,5,5,0,2,0,0,0,0),
	(2518,3018,'ESU0058',104,1,'大氣動力學（一）','Atmospheric Dynamics (I)',4522,'','','H',3,91,'',0,'3','N',0,'1','◎限大三大四修習',0,'','公館Ｃ409',NULL,'三7-9',0,'',NULL,20,0.4,3,50,3,'教學目標: 介紹大氣運動基本定理和控制方程，以及在氣象上之運用，提共未來大氣專業課程之基礎。 教學內容: 課程先簡介大氣動力學的綱要，進而教授大氣之基本概念-單位，因次化，尺度分析及標準大氣之架構。繼之介紹基本守恆定律，大氣之基本方程及應用，環流、渦度之概念以及邊界層理論；並將所學之概念應用於綜觀尺度天氣系統運動之分析。 1.Introduction, 2.The basic conservation laws, 3.Elementary applications of the basic equations, 4.Circulation and vorticity, 5.The planetary boundary layer, 6.Synoptic-scale motions I: quasi-geostrophic analysis. 實施方式: 講授 方法評量: 作業、小考、及平時成績(30%) 期中考(30%) 期末考(40%) 參考書目: An Introduction to Dynamic Meteorology. Author: James R. Holton. Fourth Edition, pp. 535. Available from 台北圖書公司, 台北市羅斯福路三段335號6樓, 02-3625376、或巨擘書局﹐懷寧街36號2樓﹐Tel: 23310940。',0,18,18,0,0,0,0,0,0),
